column_description: The ID of the airline operating the flight, which corresponds to the 'uid' column in the 'airlines' table
The unique flight number assigned to the flight by the airline
The code of the airport where the flight originates, which corresponds to the 'AirportCode' column in the 'airports' table
The code of the airport where the flight is destined, which corresponds to the 'AirportCode' column in the 'airports' table
